<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Manual Operacional — raphia.ag</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;1,9..40,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg-dark: #292b2d;
    --bg-light: #e8e7e7;
    --pink: #ff40aa;
    --purple: #600298;
    --text-on-dark: #e8e7e7;
    --text-muted-dark: rgba(232,231,231,0.55);
    --text-on-light: #292b2d;
    --text-muted-light: #5a5a5a;
    --border-dark: rgba(255,64,170,0.18);
    --border-light: rgba(41,43,45,0.14);
    --card-dark: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    --card-light: #fff;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg-light);
    color: var(--text-on-light);
    font-size: 14.5px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* CAPA */
  .cover {
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 80px 60px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cover-blob-1 {
    position: absolute;
    top: -150px; right: -150px;
    width: 500px; height: 500px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(96,2,152,0.35) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cover-blob-2 {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -100px; left: -100px;
    width: 400px; height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,64,170,0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cover-logo {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .cover-logo img {
    height: 56px;
    width: auto;
    filter: brightness(1);
  }

  .cover-pill {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--pink);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,64,170,0.4);
    padding: 6px 18px;
    border-radius: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .cover-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 54px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text-on-dark);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .cover-title span {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--pink), var(--purple));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .cover-sub {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-muted-dark);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-bottom: 70px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .cover-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 56px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,64,170,0.2);
    padding-top: 36px;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .cover-meta-item span {
    display: block;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(232,231,231,0.3);
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .cover-meta-item strong {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-on-dark);
  }

  /* TOC */
  .toc-page {
    padding: 90px 80px;
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--pink);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .page-h1 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 38px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--bg-dark);
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .toc-list { list-style: none; }

  .toc-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 16px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }

  .toc-num {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--pink);
    min-width: 26px;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .toc-text {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--bg-dark);
    flex: 1;
  }

  .toc-desc {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--text-muted-light);
    margin-top: 3px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* SECTION PAGES */
  .content-page {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 80px 80px;
  }

  .section-header {
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    margin: 0 -80px 56px;
    padding: 48px 80px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 28px;
  }

  .sh-num {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 72px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .sh-content .section-eyebrow { color: rgba(255,64,170,0.8); }

  .sh-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text-on-dark);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  /* CONTENT */
  h2.ct {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--bg-dark);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    margin-top: 48px;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--pink);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  h2.ct:first-of-type { margin-top: 0; }

  h3.cs {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--purple);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    margin-top: 30px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  }

  p.cp {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: #3a3a3a;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  /* STEPS */
  .steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; margin: 28px 0; }

  .step { display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start; position: relative; }

  .step::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 17px;
    top: 40px;
    width: 2px;
    height: calc(100% - 16px);
    background: var(--border-light);
  }
  .step:last-child::after { display: none; }

  .snum {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    color: var(--pink);
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .scontent {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    flex: 1;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .stitle {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--bg-dark);
    margin-bottom: 5px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .sdesc {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-muted-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .smeta { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; margin-top: 10px; }

  .badge {
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 2px 9px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }
  .br { background: rgba(41,43,45,0.07); color: var(--bg-dark); border: 1px solid rgba(41,43,45,0.18); }
  .bd { background: rgba(255,64,170,0.08); color: #b0006a; border: 1px solid rgba(255,64,170,0.25); }
  .bt { background: rgba(96,2,152,0.08); color: var(--purple); border: 1px solid rgba(96,2,152,0.2); }

  /* INFO CARDS */
  .igrid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 18px;
    margin: 22px 0;
  }

  .icard {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .icard-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--bg-dark);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .icard-body { font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--text-muted-light); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* TIMELINE */
  .timeline {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
    margin: 30px 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px;
    left: 36px; right: 36px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--border-light);
  }

  .tl-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; text-align: center; padding: 0 8px; }

  .tl-dot {
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    border: 2px solid var(--pink);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }

  .tl-dot span {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--pink);
  }

  .tl-period {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--pink);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .tl-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--bg-dark); font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; }

  /* HIGHLIGHT BOXES */
  .hbox {
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 26px 30px;
    margin: 28px 0;
    display: flex;
    gap: 18px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .hbox-ico { font-size: 22px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; color: var(--pink); }

  .hbox-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--pink);
    margin-bottom: 7px;
  }

  .hbox-body { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted-dark); line-height: 1.65; }

  .pbox {
    background: rgba(96,2,152,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(96,2,152,0.2);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--purple);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 18px 22px;
    margin: 18px 0;
  }

  .pbox-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--purple);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .pbox-body { font-size: 13px; color: #3a1060; line-height: 1.65; }

  /* CHECKLIST */
  .checklist { list-style: none; margin: 14px 0; }

  .checklist li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 9px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: #3a3a3a;
  }

  .checklist li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .cbox {
    width: 17px; height: 17px;
    border: 2px solid var(--purple);
    border-radius: 4px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  /* ORG CHART */
  .org-chart { margin: 28px 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }

  .org-level { display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; padding: 16px 0; }

  .org-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    text-align: center;
    min-width: 130px;
  }

  .org-card.top {
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    border-color: var(--bg-dark);
  }

  .org-card.top .org-role { color: rgba(232,231,231,0.45); }
  .org-card.top .org-title { color: var(--text-on-dark); }

  .org-card.mid { border-top: 3px solid var(--pink); }

  .org-role { font-size: 9.5px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted-light); margin-bottom: 4px; }

  .org-title { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 12.5px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--bg-dark); }

  .org-connector { width: 2px; height: 26px; background: var(--border-light); margin: 0 auto; }

  /* TWO-COL */
  .two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 22px; margin: 18px 0; }

  .week-block {
    background: #f6f5f3;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 18px 22px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--purple);
  }

  .week-block.pink { border-left-color: var(--pink); }

  .week-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--bg-dark);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .week-items { list-style: none; font-size: 13px; color: #3a3a3a; }

  .week-items li {
    padding: 5px 0;
    display: flex;
    gap: 9px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(41,43,45,0.07);
  }

  .week-items li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .week-items li::before { content: '→'; color: var(--pink); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* APPROVAL FLOW */
  .approval-flow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    margin: 22px 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .ap-step {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 13px 16px;
    text-align: center;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 110px;
  }

  .ap-label { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted-light); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .ap-name { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 12.5px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--bg-dark); }

  .ap-arrow { color: var(--pink); font-size: 18px; padding: 0 6px; flex-shrink: 0; font-weight: 700; }

  /* TABLE */
  .ttable { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 18px 0; font-size: 13px; }

  .ttable th {
    text-align: left;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: var(--text-muted-light);
    padding: 11px 14px;
    background: #f6f5f3;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-light);
  }

  .ttable td {
    padding: 12px 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    color: #3a3a3a;
    vertical-align: top;
  }

  .ttable tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .ttable td:first-child { font-weight: 600; color: var(--bg-dark); }

  /* KPI GRID */
  .kpi-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 18px; }

  .kpi-item { background: #f6f5f3; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 16px; }
  .kpi-label { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted-light); margin-bottom: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .kpi-value { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--bg-dark); }
  .kpi-change { font-size: 10.5px; color: var(--purple); margin-top: 3px; }

  .report-section { border: 1px solid var(--border-light); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; margin: 18px 0; }

  .report-header {
    background: #f6f5f3;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .report-header-title { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--bg-dark); }
  .report-body { padding: 18px 20px; }

  /* FOOTER */
  .page-footer {
    margin: 70px -80px -80px;
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    padding: 26px 80px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .footer-brand {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(232,231,231,0.5);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .footer-note { font-size: 11.5px; color: rgba(232,231,231,0.25); }

  .divider { height: 1px; background: var(--border-light); margin: 36px 0; }

  @media screen and (max-width: 700px) {
    .cover { padding: 60px 28px; }
    .cover-title { font-size: 34px; }
    .content-page { padding: 40px 24px; }
    .section-header { margin: 0 -24px 40px; padding: 36px 24px; }
    .page-footer { margin: 40px -24px -40px; padding: 22px 24px; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
    .toc-page { padding: 60px 24px; }
    .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .timeline { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .kpi-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .cover-meta { flex-direction: column; gap: 18px; }
    .approval-flow { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- CAPA -->
<div class="cover">
  <div class="cover-blob-1"></div>
  <div class="cover-blob-2"></div>
  <div class="cover-logo">
    <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="raphia.ag" style="height:52px; width:auto;" />
  </div>
  <div class="cover-pill">Manual Operacional</div>
  <h1 class="cover-title">Processos e <span>Operacoes</span><br>da Agencia</h1>
  <p class="cover-sub">Guia completo de fluxos, responsabilidades, prazos e entregaveis para todas as areas da raphia.ag.</p>
  <div class="cover-meta">
    <div class="cover-meta-item">
      <span>Versao</span>
      <strong>1.0 / 2025</strong>
    </div>
    <div class="cover-meta-item">
      <span>Aplicacao</span>
      <strong>Uso Interno</strong>
    </div>
    <div class="cover-meta-item">
      <span>Revisao</span>
      <strong>Trimestral</strong>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- TOC -->
<div class="toc-page">
  <div class="section-eyebrow">raphia.ag — Manual Operacional</div>
  <h1 class="page-h1">Sumário</h1>
  <ul class="toc-list">
    <li class="toc-item">
      <span class="toc-num">01</span>
      <div>
        <div class="toc-text">Estrutura Organizacional</div>
        <div class="toc-desc">Equipe, papeis e responsabilidades</div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="toc-item">
      <span class="toc-num">02</span>
      <div>
        <div class="toc-text">Fluxo Geral da Agencia</div>
        <div class="toc-desc">Visao macro do ciclo de vida de um cliente</div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="toc-item">
      <span class="toc-num">03</span>
      <div>
        <div class="toc-text">Onboarding do Cliente</div>
        <div class="toc-desc">Do fechamento ao inicio da operacao</div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="toc-item">
      <span class="toc-num">04</span>
      <div>
        <div class="toc-text">Criacao de Conteudo</div>
        <div class="toc-desc">Estrategia, personas, roteiros e gravacao (15 dias)</div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="toc-item">
      <span class="toc-num">05</span>
      <div>
        <div class="toc-text">Producao e Design</div>
        <div class="toc-desc">Edicao, artes, aprovacao e publicacao</div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="toc-item">
      <span class="toc-num">06</span>
      <div>
        <div class="toc-text">Trafego Pago</div>
        <div class="toc-desc">Briefing, campanhas, relatorios e otimizacao mensal</div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="toc-item">
      <span class="toc-num">07</span>
      <div>
        <div class="toc-text">Fluxo de Aprovacao</div>
        <div class="toc-desc">Revisao interna, aprovacao do cliente e publicacao</div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="toc-item">
      <span class="toc-num">08</span>
      <div>
        <div class="toc-text">Ferramentas da Agencia</div>
        <div class="toc-desc">Stack completa por setor</div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="toc-item">
      <span class="toc-num">09</span>
      <div>
        <div class="toc-text">Checklists Operacionais</div>
        <div class="toc-desc">Verificacao por etapa e entregaveis</div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="toc-item">
      <span class="toc-num">10</span>
